'''巴祝大屠杀'''（{{vie|v=Thảm sát Ba Chúc|hn=慘殺巴祝}}）是由[[紅色高棉|紅色高棉]]領導的[[柬埔寨革命軍|柬埔寨革命軍]]於1978年4月18日至4月30日在越南[[安江省|安江省]][[知宗县|知宗县]][[巴祝市鎮|巴祝社]]犯下的[[戰爭罪行|戰爭罪行]]，入侵越南的赤柬軍將當地村民押往寺廟與學校內虐殺，之後數日間逃往山內的居民也被殘酷屠殺，造成3,157人遇难，幾乎全部的被害者都是被射殺、刺殺或[[斬首|斬首]]<ref name="DSPL"/><ref name="Herald">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/01/07/opinion/07iht-edpringle_ed3_.html |title=James Pringle, "MEANWHILE: When the Khmer Rouge came to kill in Vietnam," ''The New York Times'', January 7, 2004. |access-date=2014-08-29 |archive-date=2015-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520133611/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/01/07/opinion/07iht-edpringle_ed3_.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==背景==
越南和柬埔寨的共產黨人在越南戰爭期間結盟與美國支持的政府作戰，但在獲取政權後紅色高棉領導層開始清洗自己隊伍中受過越南培訓的人員，隨後開始侵略越南<ref name="Kiernan2008">{{cite book |author=Ben Kiernan |title=Blood and Soil: Modern Genocide 1500–2000 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=R5p7cRyK748C&pg=PA548 |year=2008 |publisher=Melbourne University Publishing |isbn=978-0-522-85477-0 |pages=548–549 |access-date=2022-03-12 |archive-date=2022-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220309011215/https://books.google.com/books?id=R5p7cRyK748C&pg=PA548 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1975年5月3日，紅色高棉派军入侵[[富国岛|富国岛]]<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2YY0DwAAQBAJ&q=Ph%C3%BA+Qu%E1%BB%91c+1975+attack&pg=PA315|title=The Macabresque: Human Violation and Hate in Genocide, Mass Atrocity and Enemy-making|isbn=9780190677886|last1=Weisband|first1=Edward|year=2018|access-date=2022-03-12|archive-date=2022-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220219145519/https://books.google.com/books?id=2YY0DwAAQBAJ&q=Ph%C3%BA+Qu%E1%BB%91c+1975+attack&pg=PA315|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=isuDDwAAQBAJ&q=Ph%C3%BA+Qu%E1%BB%91c+1975+attack&pg=PA284|title=Sustainable Development Goals in Southeast Asia and ASEAN: National and Regional Approaches|date=2019-01-14|isbn=9789004391949|access-date=2022-03-12|archive-date=2022-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220219145517/https://books.google.com/books?id=isuDDwAAQBAJ&q=Ph%C3%BA+Qu%E1%BB%91c+1975+attack&pg=PA284|dead-url=no}}</ref>，随后於5月10日侵占[[土珠岛|土珠岛]]，杀害了528名平民，6月14日被[[越南人民軍|越南人民軍]]驱离<ref>{{cite news|url=https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E7%81%AD%E7%BB%9D%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A640%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%B1%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E4%B9%89%E5%8A%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%A5%96%E5%9B%BD%E9%A2%86%E5%9C%9F%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%83/90309.vnp|title=柬埔寨推翻种族灭绝制度40年：有效履行国际义务、有力维护祖国领土主权|date=2018-12-31|work=越通社|accessdate=2021-11-04|archive-date=2021-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211106222424/https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E7%81%AD%E7%BB%9D%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A640%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E5%B1%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E4%B9%89%E5%8A%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%9B%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%A5%96%E5%9B%BD%E9%A2%86%E5%9C%9F%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%83/90309.vnp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Sổ tay địa danh Kiên Giang |author=Anh Động (Hội Văn nghệ dân gian Việt Nam) |publisher=Nhà xuất bản Đại học Quốc gia Hà Nội |year=2010 |isbn=978-604-62-0291-2 |page=284}}</ref>。

儘管發生了衝突，但統一後的越南和柬埔寨的領導人在1976年期間進行了幾次公開外交交流以強調他們之間所謂的牢固關係，然而1977年3月15日至18日在[[堅江省|堅江省]]和3月25日至28日在[[安江省|安江省]]再次發生跨境襲擊，4月30日、5月17日和5月19日發生了更多襲擊，造成222名平民死亡，在5月17日的襲擊中紅色高棉砲擊了安江省的省會[[朱篤市|朱篤市]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kiernan |first1=Ben |title=New Light on the Origins of the Vietnam-Kampuchea Conflict |url=https://gsp.yale.edu/sites/default/files/newlightontheorigins.pdf |website=Yale |access-date=2022-01-30 |archive-date=2022-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217074133/https://gsp.yale.edu/sites/default/files/newlightontheorigins.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="TuoiTre">{{Cite web|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090413150455/http://www.tuoitre.com.vn/Tianyon/Index.aspx?ArticleID=310675&ChannelID=89|url=http://www.tuoitre.com.vn/Tianyon/Index.aspx?ArticleID=310675&ChannelID=89|title=Ký ức kinh hoàng về Khơme đỏ|archive-date=2009-04-11|work=Báo ''Tuổi Trẻ''|date=2009-04-11|access-date=2009-04-11|url-status=live}}</ref>。1977年9月25日中秋节，紅色高棉在柬越邊境全线发起攻击，深入[[西宁省|西宁省]]境内约10公里，杀害当地592名居民<ref>{{cite news|url=https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%8E%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9B%A2%E4%B8%8A%E9%A6%99%E7%BC%85%E6%80%80%E9%81%AD%E6%B3%A2%E5%B0%94%E5%B8%83%E7%89%B9%E5%86%9B%E6%9D%80%E5%AE%B3%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A0%E8%BE%9C%E5%B9%B3%E6%B0%91/92327.vnp|title=越南与柬埔寨妇女代表团上香缅怀遭波尔布特军杀害的无辜平民|date=2019-02-22|work=越通社|accessdate=2021-11-04|archive-date=2021-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211106223930/https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E4%B8%8E%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9B%A2%E4%B8%8A%E9%A6%99%E7%BC%85%E6%80%80%E9%81%AD%E6%B3%A2%E5%B0%94%E5%B8%83%E7%89%B9%E5%86%9B%E6%9D%80%E5%AE%B3%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A0%E8%BE%9C%E5%B9%B3%E6%B0%91/92327.vnp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==犯行==
1978年4月18日，紅色高棉軍隊越過越南邊境，包圍了邊境上的[[巴祝市鎮|巴祝社]]，切斷了通往該鎮的所有道路，隨後開始挨家挨戶搶劫貴重物品並殺死牛，然後將房屋燒毀<ref name = "VNS"/>。紅色高棉士兵將抓獲的大約800名平民圍捕到當地學校和[[三寶寺_(安江省)|三寶寺]]附近的荒地，將他們槍殺、割喉或用棍棒毆打致死，孩子們被拋到空中然後被刺刀刺死，婦女被強姦並被用木棍侵入生殖器致死<ref name="Herald"/>。4月20日，紅色高棉包圍了試圖躲在[[飛來寺_(安江省)|飛來寺]]中避難的平民，並向寺内開火，當場造成約80人死亡，40個躲在佛桌下的平民被紅色高棉投擲的手榴彈擊中，39人當場死亡，只有一位躲在角落的女子逃過一劫，剩下的一百多人試圖向紅色高棉士兵投降並立即被屠殺<ref>{{cite news |title=Về nơi dòng sông máu rùng rợn |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080506105906/http://www.qdnd.vn/qdnd/baongay.xahoi.tinxahoi.34044.qdnd |accessdate=2022-03-15 |work=báo Quân đội nhân dân}}</ref><ref name = "VNS">{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20050509134408/http://vietnamnews.vnagency.com.vn/showarticle.php?num=01TRA080505| title = The river flows quietly once again | work = Vietnam News Agency | language = en | author = Huu Ngoc | date = 2005-05-08 | url = http://vietnamnews.vnagency.com.vn/showarticle.php?num=01TRA080505| archive-date = 2005-05-09}}</ref>。許多平民從鎮上的大屠殺中逃脫並試圖躲在鎮外[[象山_(安江省)|象山]]的山洞中，紅色高棉使用追踪犬跟隨平民進入山洞，向山洞內投擲手榴彈並射殺躲藏的平民<ref>{{cite web |title=Victory over Pol Pot regime: They died for Cambodia to revive |url=https://en.vietnamplus.vn/victory-over-pol-pot-regime-they-died-for-cambodia-to-revive/154573.vnp |website=vietnam plus |access-date=2022-01-28 |archive-date=2022-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220128035533/https://en.vietnamplus.vn/victory-over-pol-pot-regime-they-died-for-cambodia-to-revive/154573.vnp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=VTC>{{cite news |title=Những trò giết người man rợ của bọn Pol Pot |url=https://vtc.vn/nhung-tro-giet-nguoi-man-ro-cua-bon-pol-pot-ar140851.html |accessdate=2022-03-16 |work=VTC News |date=2014-01-06 |archive-date=2021-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517233705/https://vtc.vn/nhung-tro-giet-nguoi-man-ro-cua-bon-pol-pot-ar140851.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。到4月30日，紅色高棉在越南軍隊趕來之前從巴祝社撤退，留下的地雷造成約200人死傷<ref>{{cite book |last1=Bartrop |first1=Paul |title=Cambodian Genocide: The Essential Reference Guide |date=2022-02-28 |page=47 |url=https://www.google.com/books/edition/Cambodian_Genocide_The_Essential_Referen/unhXEAAAQBAJ?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=Ba+Ch%C3%BAc&pg=PA5&printsec=frontcover |access-date=2022-03-21}}</ref>。到大屠殺結束時，已有3,157名平民喪生<ref name = "Herald"/><ref>{{cite news |title=The forgotten massacre Killing Fields in Vietnam recalled by few |url=https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/forgotten-massacre-killing-fields-vietnam-recalled-few |access-date=2022-01-24 |agency=phnompenhpost |date=2013-04-19 |archive-date=2022-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220125024151/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/forgotten-massacre-killing-fields-vietnam-recalled-few |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

大屠殺的幸存者阮文敬講述：“我的妻子，四個孩子和六個孫輩都被殺了，開槍前他們強迫我們交出所有的珠寶和財產，我醒來時環顧四周，當我看到我的外孫女抱著我親愛的女兒的乳房一動不動地躺在血泊中時，我傻眼了。”他在黑夜的掩護下從一堆屍體中爬出來躲進象山的一個山洞裡，那時“那些被波爾布特殘害的人的悲鳴聲並沒有停止”<ref name="TuoiTre"/>。另一名幸存者何氏娥與父母、兄弟姐妹、丈夫和六個孩子一起被擄到邊境附近遭到殘酷毆打，她的小女兒頭部被鐵棍連續擊中3次，尖叫著“媽媽！媽媽！救救我！”當她恢復意識時，全家人都死了<ref name="Herald"/>。和父母逃到三寶寺的女孩阮氏玉霜和在寺内避難的村民被紅色高棉趕到廟外的荒地，在那裏他們被集體槍殺，阮氏玉霜被子彈擊中頭部，但未造成致命傷，紅色高棉撤離後躲在屍體堆中的她被救到醫院<ref>{{cite news |title=Tội ác Pol Pot: Cô bé ngủ bên xác cha 12 ngày sau cuộc tàn sát |url=https://www.doisongphapluat.com/toi-ac-pol-pot-co-be-ngu-ben-xac-cha-12-ngay-sau-cuoc-tan-sat-a5312.html |accessdate=2022-03-16 |work=ĐSPL |date=2013-10-17}}</ref>。

==後續==
1978年底，[[波尔布特|波尔布特]]动用十个师团準備再次發起侵略越南的战争，在此背景下，1978年12月7日，越共中央政治局、中央军委通过了討伐波尔布特集团的決定，越南人民軍迅速[[柬越戰爭|擊潰赤柬軍隊]]，推翻了波爾布特政權，終結了[[紅色高棉大屠殺|紅色高棉大屠殺]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E5%90%B4%E6%98%A5%E5%8E%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%86%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%97%E8%BE%B9%E5%A2%83%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BF%9D%E5%8D%AB%E6%88%98%E8%83%9C%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E6%8D%8D%E5%8D%AB%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%83%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E6%95%99%E8%AE%AD/90565.vnp|title=吴春历大将：越南西南边境地区保卫战胜利是捍卫国家主权事业的经验教训|date=2019-01-07|work=越通社|accessdate=2021-12-25|archive-date=2021-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211106223935/https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E5%90%B4%E6%98%A5%E5%8E%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%86%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%97%E8%BE%B9%E5%A2%83%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BF%9D%E5%8D%AB%E6%88%98%E8%83%9C%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E6%8D%8D%E5%8D%AB%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%83%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E6%95%99%E8%AE%AD/90565.vnp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=越南西南边境地区保卫战胜利 帮助柬埔寨人民摆脱种族灭绝制度 |url=https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E5%9B%BE%E8%A1%A8%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%97%E8%BE%B9%E5%A2%83%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BF%9D%E5%8D%AB%E6%88%98%E8%83%9C%E5%88%A9-%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E7%81%AD%E7%BB%9D%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6/90460.vnp |accessdate=2022-03-20 |agency=越通社 |date=2019-01-04 |archive-date=2022-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511223017/https://zh.vietnamplus.vn/%E5%9B%BE%E8%A1%A8%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%97%E8%BE%B9%E5%A2%83%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BF%9D%E5%8D%AB%E6%88%98%E8%83%9C%E5%88%A9-%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E7%81%AD%E7%BB%9D%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6/90460.vnp }}</ref>。

戰爭結束後，1979年安江省政府在巴祝社為遇難者建立了陵園，每年的农历三月十五和十六为死難者举行集体祭祀仪式，1980年7月10日，越南政府將遇難者陵園和用作屠殺的三寳寺和飛來寺列為國家級歷史遺蹟<ref name="VNS"/><ref name=3d>{{cite news |title=An Giang: Lễ giỗ tập thể các nạn nhân trong vụ thảm sát Ba Chúc |url=https://www.vietnamplus.vn/an-giang-le-gio-tap-the-cac-nan-nhan-trong-vu-tham-sat-ba-chuc/320737.vnp |accessdate=2022-03-20 |agency=越通社 |date=2015-05-04 |archive-date=2022-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511223016/https://www.vietnamplus.vn/an-giang-le-gio-tap-the-cac-nan-nhan-trong-vu-tham-sat-ba-chuc/320737.vnp }}</ref>，2011年安江省撥款300亿越南盾對遇難者陵園進行重修，陵園占地5公顷，包括面积500平方米的墓室和展示現場图片及实物的紀念館<ref name=3d/>。紀念館中展示現場照片和紅色高棉用來進行大屠殺的長矛、棍棒等凶器<ref>{{cite web |title=Ba Chuc Tomb |url=https://www.lonelyplanet.com/vietnam/mekong-delta/chau-doc/attractions/ba-chuc-tomb/a/poi-sig/1527131/357891 |website=Lonely Planet |access-date=2022-01-29 |archive-date=2022-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220129052438/https://www.lonelyplanet.com/vietnam/mekong-delta/chau-doc/attractions/ba-chuc-tomb/a/poi-sig/1527131/357891 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Vietnam |date= |publisher=National Geographic Society (2006) |page=223 |url=https://www.google.com/books/edition/Vietnam/9WLfsdeJgHsC?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=Ba+Ch%C3%BAc+massacre&pg=PA233&printsec=frontcover |access-date=2022-01-29}}</ref>，墓室存放著1,159名無人收殓的大屠殺遇難者的遺骨，其中1,017個頭骨已按年齡和性別鑑定<ref name=3d/>，包括嬰兒29人，16~20歲女孩88人，21~44歲女性155人，41~60歲女性103人，60歲以上女性86人，16~20歲男性23人，21~40歲男性79人，41~60歲男性162人，60歲以上男性38人<ref name="DSPL">{{Cite web|url=http://www.doisongphapluat.com/to-quoc-xanh/kham-pha/ron-nguoi-nha-mo-nan-nhan-pon-pot-o-an-giang-a8201.html|title=Rợn người nhà mồ nạn nhân Pôn Pốt ở An Giang|date=2013-11-08|work=Báo ''Đời sống và Pháp luật''|access-date=2015-09-04|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814082803/https://www.doisongphapluat.com/to-quoc-xanh/kham-pha/ron-nguoi-nha-mo-nan-nhan-pon-pot-o-an-giang-a8201.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其餘遇難者遺體或是已被親人埋葬，或是還遺留在象山的山洞中，因為有些洞太深，無法將遺體抬出來，親人們只好用土把洞填滿<ref name=VTC/><ref>{{cite book |author1=Ngày tháng |title=con số thương vong trong vụ thảm sát Ba Chúc |publisher=安江省人民委員會 |page=300-301}}</ref>。

